snippet.title: Demon's Tier+ - Launch Trailer | PS4  PS Vita
snippet.description:
Now available on PS4 & PS Vita! (crossbuy)

Dungeon-RPG roguelike with arcade and adventure elements. Enter the dungeons of King Thosgar and destroy his demonic minions!

Combining the best elements from Xenon Valkyrie+ and Riddled Corpses EX, this is the latest game in the Diabolical Mind trilogy!
